name: Skull Away
description:
A skeleton wakes up on a cemetery during a Halloween. 

Now he has a new chance to live, but be careful! Other monsters came back to life too. 

Find the key and make your way out of the cemetery

////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////

Use the arrows or wasd to walk and space to pause.

The background is a pre-made asset, the other stuff were made by me during the time spam of the jam.
